message.entry: Unable to create parallel.pool.Constant on the workers.
The parallel.pool.Constant contains a Composite value. Accessing a Composite value within a parallel.pool.Constant from the MATLAB client is not supported.
A parallel.pool.Constant requires a Composite that has a value defined on every worker.
The two-argument parallel.pool.Constant constructor requires two function handles.
Unable to retrieve 'Value' field because the parallel.pool.Constant is invalid.
